### 🔬 ACADEMIC ATTRIBUTION & CITATION 
Users of this framework, particularly those applying the identified **Dimensionless Control Parameters**, are requested to cite the following primary discovery markers:

* **Critical Phase Transition Threshold ($\mathcal{K}_c$):** The observed bifurcation point at $\approx 1.441$ within the informational density functional.
* **Stochastic Residence Constant ($P_c$):** The asymptotic mean of $0.0512$ identified in homeostatic neurodynamic state-space.

**Formal Citation Format:**
> Nicoletti, D. L. (2026). ASHI-CORE: Manifold Dynamics and Phase Transitions in Dissipative Systems. Zenodo. https://doi.org/[INSERIRE_IL_TUO_DOI_QUI]

